author: cbs8
title: Petco opens new headquarters in Rancho Bernardo
text:
SAN DIEGO (CBS 8) - Petco is showed off it's new digs Wednesday morning.
The company is held it's grand opening ceremony at its new 300,000 square foot headquarters in Rancho Bernardo.
The new facility will help support Petco's 1300 stores. The new campus will house 650 employees, pet play areas, aquatic life, animal habitats, a walking trail and a dog park.
